high_descs: Turn around, walk to the side of the table with coffee machine
Grab the fork on the table
Turn left, walk to the sink
Put the fork in the left sink, turn on faucet, wash the fork with water, turn off the faucet, take the fork
Turn around, walk to the white table
Put the fork down on the table
anns.task_desc: Wash the fork on the table, put it on the white table

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the fridge, then turn left and walk over to the end of the white table.
Pick up the closest metal fork off of the white table.
Turn left and walk up to the kitchen sink.
Place the metal fork in the left sink basin and clean it, the pick it back up.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk over to the front of the white table.
Place the metal fork in a vertical manner on the table in front of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean metal fork on the white table.

high_descs: Go to the table with the coffee machine.
Pick up the fork from the table.
Bring the fork to the sink.
Clean the fork in the sink.
Bring the fork back to the table.
Put the fork on the table in front of the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned fork on the table.
